Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污穢的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其自身的罪而滅亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位現在還年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與「污穢」是無緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是肩負新世界的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 雖然我比不上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個被完全玷污的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起行動以後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想淨化之前犯下的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 請引導我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混沌的彼岸的新世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再頂嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 讓我們師生同心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.36,0:00:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好痛
;Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/OP

Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說多少遍才明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,0)\an8\fs28}ACT 11  屍嵐颳起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「殺人病」完全就是扯淡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是政府查不到屍體襲擊人類的原因而找的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是應對恐慌的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大家最喜聞樂見的「日本的顧慮」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說屍體真的在到處晃悠了嗎 愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是新型的傳染病 錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 怎麼可能無端端就發生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這麼認為也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一群小白想查明真相？ 少來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓專家在可以靜下來研究的環境下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花長時間去研究
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事 我們根本做不來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你們自己能做到啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼想活命就別被<喪屍>咬到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有比這個更重要的了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做 爸爸已經告訴你們了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是你想說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就奇怪為啥高中生會濫用槍械
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護什麼的 只是嘴上說說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這班傢伙想用暴力讓我們屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明世界變成這樣 亞洲有無數人受苦受難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥會冒出個亞洲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我們去做殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 強迫我們的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將殺人合理化的 那個男人的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你到底在說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩不准插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩… 也不想想我們是怎麼熬過…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是由大人決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剝削階級的豬和沉迷暴力的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是熱愛和平的大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們嚴正拒絕暴力支配！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴正拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城…你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.74,0:04:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到爸爸的壞話 一激動就跟他們槓上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 他們難道什麼都沒看到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是緊閉雙眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微能理解…他們的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是找罵啊 死肥仔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們對不想見到的東西 都想裝沒看見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不想自己被否定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大部分人明知道出了事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會行動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在他們不得不承認發生變化了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.18,0:05:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時他們的第一反應是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時 就算一開始就知道不會順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不承認變化 就不用承認自己的過錯和愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在學校出事後 想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 稍微對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上了一課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不好意思 我可是很坦率地在承認啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 所以才會這麼想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.34,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才有資格當領隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說毒島老師的千金 作為劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起千葉佐那子有過之而無不及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an7}註：千葉佐那子 北辰一刀流千葉周作之弟千葉定吉的長女\N北辰一刀流免許皆傳 劍術了得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦即是位清純婀娜的日本少女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使直接觸碰 亦不會玷污此刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實稀罕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彎度輕微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刃紋並未浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋒兩刃 小烏造
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小銃兼正…我認為是村田刀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明治中葉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為「村田銃」而知名的村田少將
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在東京炮兵工廠所造的其中一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說砍豬骨能一刀兩斷 刀刃絲毫不缺口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一飽眼福了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它已歸你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自知無禮 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無正當理由 我不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.89,0:08:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾受毒島老師指點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃謝禮 這個回答你滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這刀應贈予父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是毒島家的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有如實相告了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子的膚淺智慧 讓您見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你已猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於我那不成器的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖曾救過她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也多虧了她 才能倖免於難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.48,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼想保護她 讓她待在身邊不更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高城家千金 由衷敬愛父母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說我們父女太相似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者交付給孝…小室 而不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他才是我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他自小我便認識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也知道他長成了一個好青年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你如此信賴他 更說明了這點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得出他現在還有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在非常時期領導人們的應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算推我當領隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上就這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗 沒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己 反而會留手尾的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很依賴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也很勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校也是 其他時候也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是豁出去罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒什麼優點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論戰鬥 強手有冴子姐和平野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算得上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 沙耶夠醒目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜香老師怎麼說也是個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教你一條女生的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可愛的男生 或者是會寵自己的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其他更重要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兩邊都不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定以前是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.95,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算嘴上說些很絕望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了關鍵時刻 會勇敢地跳出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.24,0:11:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要任何理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為你知道必須這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂的 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我沒察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定之前就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…肯定就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跟你在一起 我可以做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你喜歡上其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣做 我就活不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是該高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是該生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太現實了 這理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是這麼現實
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛吧 還是應該好好躺躺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓老師看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好想想我那番話的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到氣息 就在等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒聽見聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐也跟他說說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計阿孝會更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能別叫我學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別提這事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想想起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生還者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從學校逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 求求你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上解除路障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要去找家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 父親出遠門了 只能祈求他沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過母親從騷亂開始推算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在荷床第三小學上班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗的… 宮本的父親是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去東區警署的話 應該會明白事情緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她母親應該據守在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去搜救以後 你又有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們後天清早就要出發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在留在都市部太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在時限之前找齊人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人數太多的話 照顧不過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時如果家人需要幫助 我會留下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到了出發時間我還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請你當我已經決心留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身打扮也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是一直都在算著時機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然呆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冴…冴子姐 雖然感覺相當不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你準備得也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該幫得上忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 就算要帶上家人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一定程度的人數 是無法引導的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦…麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到這時會救到紫藤議員的少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這狀況 沒工夫去想選舉的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我只是一介教師罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶存活的學生逃離學校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 這是教師的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是受令尊的熏陶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老頭是國會議員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.14,0:16:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個暴君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓媽媽受苦 最後逼到她自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我這個離開家 當上教師的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床主有個很煩的公安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他女兒似乎在你學校上學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她留級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做那傢伙也會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能救我的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真偉大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮…宮本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知不知道為什麼我長槍術那麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我也學了槍劍術啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縣警大賽中從未輸過的爸爸教的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我爸受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個無論何事都不會動搖的人哭著向我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為自己而害得我留級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能操縱成績的 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我忍住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.01,0:17:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我聽說 只要爸爸調查順利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能逮捕你和紫藤議員了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你想殺人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還…還想當罪犯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟這人的父親打過些交道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在已經沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望的話 就殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冴子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須由宮本自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我 只要你還活著就被這事實折磨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我這個教師 能給你最棒的教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.51,0:18:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的判斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不值得我殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那些被你教壞了的學生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.12,0:19:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長 收到新的緊急行動命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代碼666Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代碼666Delta
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對目標November Kilo及Romeo Charlie的Doomsday命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.1立刻到發令所
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認了嗎 No.1
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長發令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統命令已經最終確認
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦將實施對November Kilo及Romeo Charlie的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.69,0:20:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的總統到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個接一個變成怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是從能源部部長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天是國土安全部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過已經被咬了呢 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒人知道何時會發生何事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的天使們 還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 寬恕我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 拯救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire One！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(405,307)\bord0\shad0}屍嵐颳起
;Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,/ED 

Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 不只是美國
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯也發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯？ 還有工夫發射導彈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跟在我們後頭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是MIRV
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an7}註：MIRV 分導式多彈頭 核武器
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然數量少 大都市和軍事基地會全滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 現在的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活死人之後是先制核打擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在好萊塢的話 這劇本不會被採用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 似乎被採用了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 上帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.04,0:23:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(410,436)\fs20}Armageddon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電磁脈衝？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}到…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EMP攻擊 我們用不了電子儀器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}就是說現在我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關門
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.27,0:23:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}小耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}沒完沒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是阿拉莫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}平野 女兒就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.00,0:23:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 夜晚將會成為真正的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.95,0:23:40.94,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(411,307)\bord0\shad0}全屍來襲.


